{"tid":1959944,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家贊成餐廳管制措施在14日有效期後(即4月11日)取消嗎?","createTime":"2020-04-05T20:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T16:09:06.000Z","uid":166360,"like":15,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca4b916c8afeb693fc003da6d0b7f31e4e6636f","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T20:08:44.000Z","msg":"現時餐廳管制措施如下:<br />\n1. 規定所有食肆入座不可超過5成<br />\n2. 每枱最多只可坐4人<br />\n3. 每張餐桌間必需相隔1.5米或設下阻隔<br />\n措施理論上可降低感染肺炎風險，不過對食肆收入帶來重大打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />贊成<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},{"pid":"40f39883963170969969e5bc8addb7084d692408","tid":1959944,"uid":136119,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T20:14:44.000Z","msg":"其實呢個措施係好<br />\n只係on9黑警亂撚咁執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f943dd2257a55ab20845e00453953c5116153911","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"措施延長到4月23號"},{"pid":"90e6f64805de7c38658bf41a06d809e0362e6bee","tid":1959944,"uid":46128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"最好即刻取消，全面開關，復課復市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bf5c81f5a471353dce4b635ff12bc23217f096","tid":1959944,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"凸手辦上黎收風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d23783a9603f00f1020a1d51947e16d4b18452","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64bf5c81f5a471353dce4b635ff12bc23217f096","tid":1959944,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"凸手辦上黎收風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"d527a75be78f10b3d939d362fd2c05d2d26e7fa5","tid":1959944,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:46:58.000Z","msg":"支持取消"},{"pid":"a9d4b6eb2544d152578a3b028efd45c20c605c18","tid":1959944,"uid":280329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"都唔撚知整黎做乜撚野<br />\n一係就叫哂全部餐廳收皮算啦<br />\n鋪又比人開 但入去食野就要比狗咬?"},{"pid":"2978d74dc09fda5f42491b91b83158502379e612","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"本港多13人確診 當中一男子感染源頭未明<br />\n09.04.2020 16:44<br />\n<br />\n本港今日新增13宗新型冠狀病毒確診病例，累計確診宗數增至973宗。新增患者包括8男5女，年齡由21至66歲，當中3人沒有外遊紀錄，包括一名到過灣仔Centre Stage酒吧的男子。早前確診的40日大男嬰的，他的37歲爸爸亦都確診，相信是從家人身上感染。亦有一名與家人同住上環的43歲男患者，感染源頭暫時未明，衛生防護中心指他從事資訊科技行業，平時活動不太多，有到信德中心外慢跑及到區內快餐店食飯，本月3日是最後一天到利園一期上班，翌日發燒，昨日入住瑪麗醫院。<br />\n<br />\n其餘10名新增患者，全部有外遊紀錄，包括兩名海外留學生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279786&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279786%26csid%3D261_341&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=a51a8335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279786&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n疫情進一步受控，餐廳管制措施應該立刻取消"},{"pid":"aa17d491ebbfd7f5759e909864baec40b5d216a3","tid":1959944,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"反對啦屌<br />\n大把人買黃店外賣<br />\n藍店粥水都冇撚得你食呀"},{"pid":"73ab8eef04f71cb75305bc81c8e922c4f2df11d3","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa17d491ebbfd7f5759e909864baec40b5d216a3","tid":1959944,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"反對啦屌<br />\n大把人買黃店外賣<br />\n藍店粥水都冇撚得你食呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以去黃店堂食?"},{"pid":"ead5a4bb296b24a18884ffbff2986efb6648dee2","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"今日只得4宗確診，證明病毒快被打敗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwSiBPB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwSiBPB.png&h=ca18ba10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e9adf731fbac9d1c52458fdb4fd16add136a5d1","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:57:55.000Z","msg":"政府應該宣布全面取消限制人群措施<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1972035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1972035</a>"},{"pid":"7511dece4341478a4d5b0495baad769073307e72","tid":1959944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"睇來考DSE真係大過天，甚至比促進經濟發展更重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全香港市民要因為DSE而無得做gym/yoga、唱K、睇戲、去酒吧、一大班人聚餐派對等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n禁聚令於文憑試開考前夕屆滿 政府大機會延2周至5月初<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1978355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1978355</a>"}]}